rmp.university: University of North Carolina at Chapel Hill
comments: This is the best freshman seminar ever! You really explored yourself and personal boundaries. Professor Page is loosy-goosy with her guidelines for photos, so you have alot of freedom in making your photos. It was fun.

Super enthusiastic and fun. Always helpful and open to everything. Likes work to be a bit edgy. Crits to makes you better not a bunch of fluff. Overall awesome woman. Take anything from her that you can.
I took professional seminar. It was literally a breeze. I don't see how you could get anything less than an A.
